I have always been passionate about unlocking the potential of human creativity and empowering creators and listeners through technology, and envision myself contributing my talent to furthering Spotify's mission to give a million creative artists the opportunity to live off their art and billions of fans the opportunity to enjoy and be inspired by it. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

